  "title": "CARPENTER",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Perform carpentry tasks related to commercial and residential projects</li>\n  <li>Assemble and install frameworks, roofing, partitions, staircases, and cabinetry</li>\n  <li>Interpret and analyze blueprints, sketches, or building plans</li>\n  <li>Measure, cut, and assemble wood, plywood, and other materials</li>\n  <li>Construct, install, and repair structures and fixtures such as doors, windows, walls, floors, frameworks, and furniture &amp; Use hand tools and power tools such as saws, hammers, drills, and chisels</li>\n  <li>Shape or cut materials to specified measurements using measuring tools</li>\n  <li>Ensure structures meet building codes and safety standards</li>\n  <li>Maintain tools and equipment in good working condition</li>\n  <li>Work with other trades to complete construction projects</li>\n  <li>Ensure quality workmanship and adherence to deadlines</li>\n</ul>",
